事故并未造成人员伤亡。比哈尔邦首席部长尼蒂什·库马尔下令对倒塌事件进行调查，并要求找出事件的责任人。 印媒指出，坍塌的桥是比哈尔邦政府最雄心勃勃的项目之一，长度达 3160 米，耗资 171 亿卢比（约 14.7 元亿人民币），原本预计将在 11 月至 12 月左右落成。 据悉，去年 4 月底，该桥也曾发生过坍塌。大桥再次坍塌引发了人们对建筑材料质量的质疑。印度耗资百亿卢比的大桥又塌了，还是当地最雄心勃勃的项目之一"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1d52d99ab5a12a0239ab46c9b5e81a4d_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604825403"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIhtKqg+rMw/0nEAMaCDk2Njg1ODA5IOnv9KMGMAk48gFAD3IJNjA0ODI1NDAzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1686011849.7053134", "card_id": "Q_603949196", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 136}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 6 月 6 日召开的 2023 苹果全球开发者大会「WWDC23」，有哪些值得关注的信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-e4a551c26798e39406a1f08f5c61b3c4_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/603949196"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIhtKqg+rMw/0nEAMaCDk2NDkxMTY1IMHH2KMGMAg42gJAEHIJNjAzOTQ5MTk2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1686011849.7057984", "card_id": "Q_604871143", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 227}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "华为已申请 GPT 相关商标，此前曾表示「底层技术不比 ChatGPT 少」，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日有媒体报道，华为 7 月 7 日将发布一款直接对标 ChatGPT 的多模态千亿级大模型产品，名为「盘古 Chat」。 据中国商标网显示，华为技术有限公司于近期申请注册了两枚「HUAWEI NETGPT」商标，国际分类为科学仪器、网站服务，当前商标状态为申请中。此外，华为已成功注册多枚「盘古」「PANGU」商标。 市场方面，ChatGPT 概念活跃，截至 6 月 5 日 13 点 59 分，ChatGPT 概念板块指数报 1698.253 点，涨幅达 2%，成交 545.60 亿元，换手率 4.11%。 此前，据中国证券报，5 月 26 日，在中关村论坛现场，针对中国证券报记者提问华为是否有信心去承载 ChatGPT 这类规模的应用，华为昇腾计算业务 CTO 周斌回应称，完全没有问题。「我们已经服务了国内几十家合作伙伴的大模型，至少从底层技术软硬件的规模上来讲，华为不比 ChatGPT 少，ChatGPT 所需的算力需求，我们已经经过了大规模验证，是完全没问题的。」周斌表示。华为版 ChatGPT 要来了？已申请商标！华为：底层技术不比 ChatGPT 少，算力完全没问题！ | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3ff67c51d3a42f7cf9bbbb41192721c8_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "33 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604871143"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhtKqg+rMw/0nEAMaCDk2Njk1ODk1IK+W9qMGMDM4jQNAEXIJNjA0ODcxMTQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1686011849.7067273", "card_id": "Q_24769341", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 138}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中国什么地方最安全不会地震？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中国很多地震带，什么地方是可以不受这些地震带波及的？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-85b3a3aa319ddaafceb3e041da4bc145_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "33 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/24769341"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IhtKqg+rMw/0nEAMaBzIwODk2NzkggKmNnwUwATipA0AScggyNDc2OTM0MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1686011849.707535", "card_id": "Q_604528233", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 73}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2023 年人工智能成为热门产业，电子信息专业今年会成为高考报考的「爆款」方向吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-959f2c07ffdba3aa4b10de4d926d849f_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "32 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604528233"}}, "att