估值为 10 亿美元。 这是什么概念？就是说，Character.AI 成为了为数不多的和 OpenAI 一个级别的 AI 独角兽。 首周下载量碾压 ChatGPT！谷歌 20 年老员工叛逃，创立第二个 OpenAI？_ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-4191b7e5c9374707e9280b5f7f293843_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604552431"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIhtKqg+rMw/0nEAMaCDk2NjI1MjExIJKA6qMGMAo4hQZAFXIJNjA0NTUyNDMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1686011849.7101781", "card_id": "Q_604132619", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 188}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《狂飙》中穷苦出身的程程，考上了名牌大学，在大公司身居要职，如此励志的人，为什么最后死得那么惨？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "程程的人设，应该是我命由我不由天的职场女强人，怎么可以死得那么窝囊？关于她的结局，我不高兴！我不服气！我要抗议！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ad09f3171f9cdaed62022fbb99c359f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604132619"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhtKqg+rMw/0nEAMaCDk2NTMxODk5IMfE3aMGMA84hANAFnIJNjA0MTMyNjE5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1686011849.7108555", "card_id": "Q_604740780", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 136}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果自由的代价是孤独，你愿意接受吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "22 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604740780"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhtKqg+rMw/0nEAMaCDk2NjY3MDEzINfA8aMGMAM4rQFAF3IJNjA0NzQwNzgweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", 